{"type":"message","id":"2d1be483","parentId":"5fb146ea","timestamp":"2026-03-09T19:50:46.474Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see - the ENOENT errors are not from our scripts, they're from the agent's own operations. The agent is trying to read files and failing. This is not something we can fix by modifying scripts - the agent itself needs to use safe read operations.\n\nThe key insight is:\n1. The Safe Functions library exists (safe-read.sh, safe-edit.sh)\n2. We've fixed 40 scripts to load Safe Functions\n3. But the agent itself (the LLM) is not using these functions - it's calling the `read` and `edit` tools directly\n4. When those tools fail (ENOENT), they report the error\n\nSo the issue is that:\n1. The `read` tool is being called on files that don't exist\n2. The agent (LLM) doesn't check if files exist before reading\n3. This causes ENOENT errors\n\nThe fix we made (adding Safe Functions to scripts) won't help because the LLM doesn't call those scripts - it calls the tools directly.\n\nLet me check what files are being accessed that don't exist.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## M — Memory（记忆写入）"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7a1b1dd93ec846d2841a8035","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"### 下次执行\n**时间**: 2026-03-10 04:00（12 分钟后）\n**任务**: 子任务 18.2 验证 Edit 匹配错误下降\n\n---\n\n## 03:48 - 子任务 18.1 验证 ENOENT 错误（⚠️ 反弹）\n\n### 验证方式\n- **时间**: 凌晨 03:48\n- **数据来源**: Session 日志（最近 6 小时和 1 小时）\n\n### 验证结果\n\n| 时间范围 | ENOENT 错误 | 目标 | 状态 |\n|---------|-----------|------|------|\n| 最近 6 小时 | **505** | <300 | ❌ **未达标** |\n| 最近 1 小时 | **166** | - | 📈 **反弹** |\n\n### 对比分析\n\n| 指标 | Round 297 | 当前（03:48） | 变化 | 趋势 |\n|------|-----------|--------------|------|------|\n| ENOENT 错误 | 471 | **505** | **+34 (+7.2%)** | 🔴 **反弹** |\n\n### 根因分析\n\n**问题根源**：\n1. ❌ **Safe Functions 未被实际使用**\n   - 我们修复了 40 个脚本，但 LLM 不调用这些脚本\n   - LLM 直接调用 `read` 和 `edit` 工具，绕过了 Safe Functions\n\n2. 🔍 **主要错误来源**：\n   - TASKS.md（12 次）- 可能是文件锁定或并发访问\n   - memory/2026-03-09.md（4 次）\n   - memory/2026-03-10.md（2 次）\n\n3. ⚠️ **修复策略错误**：\n   - 修复脚本不能解决问题\n   - 需要修复工具调用层面的逻辑\n\n### 关键发现\n\n**Safe Functions 使用情况**：\n```\n=== 最近 1 小时 Safe Functions 使用 ===\n（无记录 - Safe Functions 未被调用）\n```\n\n**结论**：修复脚本对 ENOENT 错误**无效果**，因为 LLM 不调用这些脚本。\n\n### 建议\n\n**正确修复方向**：\n1. 在工具调用前添加文件存在性检查\n2. 修改 `read` 工具的默认行为（自动检查文件是否存在）\n3. 使用 `file_exists` 检查后再调用 `read`\n\n### 下个子任务\n**任务**: 18.2 验证 Edit 匹配错误下降（预期也会反弹）","oldText":"### 下次执行\n**时间**: 2026-03-10 03:45（12 分钟后）\n**任务**: 修复第 4 批（16 个脚本，16 个问题）","path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-10.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":13207,"output":871,"cacheRead":124864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138942,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773085818542}}
